ActNational Capital Act
SubjectRitchie Feed and Seed Inc., 1740 Woodroffe Avenue, Ottawa - Lease extension
PrecisApproval for the National Capital Commission to grant a lease longer than five years by granting a ten-year extension, starting June 1, 2011, and a five-year renewal option, starting June 1, 2021, to an existing five-year lease.
